TITLE: Installing cssnano and PostCSS Dependencies
DESCRIPTION: Command to install cssnano and PostCSS as development dependencies in a Node.js project.
SOURCE: https://github.com/cssnano/cssnano/blob/master/site/src/docs/getting-started.md#2025-04-21_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: shell
CODE:
```
npm install cssnano postcss --save-dev
```

----------------------------------------

TITLE: Configuring SVGO Options in cssnano Preset
DESCRIPTION: This example demonstrates how to set options for the SVGO plugin within cssnano's preset configuration. It shows how to override specific SVGO settings in postcss.config.js.
SOURCE: https://github.com/cssnano/cssnano/blob/master/site/src/docs/presets.md#2025-04-21_snippet_5

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
module.exports = {
    plugins: [
        require('cssnano')({
            preset: ['default', {
                svgo: {
                    plugins: [{
                        name: 'preset-default',
                        params: {
                            overrides: {
                                removeDoctype: false,
                            },
                        },
                    }],
                },
            }],
        }),
    ],
};
```

