TITLE: Eleventy Front Matter Configuration
DESCRIPTION: YAML front matter configuration for generating documentation pages dynamically based on optimization data. Sets up pagination, permalink structure, and layout template.
SOURCE: https://github.com/cssnano/cssnano/blob/master/site/src/docs/optimisations/optimisation-page.md#2025-04-21_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: yaml
CODE:
```
---
pagination:
  data: optimisations
  size: 1
  alias: optimisation
permalink: '/docs/optimisations/{{ optimisation.shortName | lower }}/'
layout: 'layouts/NoSidebar.njk'
eleventyComputed:
  title: '{{ optimisation.shortName }}'
---
```

